@Comment:	Time is 0:03
@Comment:	context notes say Mot and Chi sit at table. Chi reads haltingly but is very persistent. When Chi encounters a word she doesn't know , she sounds it out with good results. There is a lot of noise and other distractions in the background , but Chi is focused on the reading. Mot is impatient at times with her corrections of Chi. Mot's main strategy is to point to the word on the page and repeat it correctly for Chi
